p Similar to 
  code new Date(Number)
  | , you can create a moment by passing an integer value representing the 
  | number of milliseconds since the Unix Epoch (1 January 1970 00:00:00 UTC).
pre var day = moment(1318781876406);
p
  span.label.label-info Note:
  |  To create a 
  code moment()
  | from a Unix timetamp (the number of seconds since the Epoch), use 
  code moment.unix(Number)
  | .
